<i>adjective</i>: 화통하다 [화통하다], 화끈하다 [화끈하다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt>화통하다 [화통하다]</dt><br>
<dd>broad-minded; outspoken; unhesitating; energetic</dd><br>
<dd>성격이나 목소리 등이 시원시원하고 마음이 넓다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's personality being generous or straightforward, or one's voice sounding powerful.</dd><br>
<dt>화끈하다 [화끈하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. burning; glowing</dd><br>
<dd>열을 받아서 갑자기 뜨거워지는 느낌이 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Feeling suddenly hot, being exposed to heat or one's face becoming suddenly hot and turning red.</dd><br>
<dd>2. unhesitating; without reserve; unhindered; outspoken</dd><br>
<dd>일을 처리하는 방식이나 성격이 매우 시원스럽다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's way of handling a task or personality being very unhesitating without reserve.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>